{
  "stem": "12462.6",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So by that time, most of the work had been done in a-- a preliminary sense.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And what had to be done back in Washington-- where we worked in the Pentagon-- we had a small office in the Pentagon-- the main problem was taking what these 50 people had, and I had, worked on in Nuremberg, and-- and brought over to Washington, and condensing it still more, because we knew we couldn't have more than 15 volumes.",
      "word_count": 61
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It wouldn't be practical in the sense of their being read by a lot of people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the judge-advocate, or the Army would not have approved printing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was a very costly business, to-- to print 1,000 volumes or more of volumes that large.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Those volumes are all 1,000 pages or more.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I left the Army, in the sense of being an officer, while I was in Nuremberg.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the reason simply was that, by that time, General Taylor was hiring [CLEARS THROAT] some of his principal deputies at supergrade levels.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that-- that amount of income was a great deal more than what I was getting as a captain.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I, having had overseas service, I had no problem getting released from the Army and accepting a job as a GS-15, and later a GS-16, which is a supergrade.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And paid me very well.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I beg your pardon?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Nuremberg.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After I'd finished doing the editing of these things?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Say that again, I didn't-- I'm not hearing you.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[CLEARS THROAT] When the Eisenhower administration came in, why, we went out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were succeeded by a new administration.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] well, I should-- should go back one, because I was-- there was something I omitted.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
